text: Jaffueliobryum is a genus of moss in family Ptychomitriaceae. ==Species== It contains the following species: * Jaffueliobryum arsenei — endemic to Mexico. ==See also== * ==References== Category:Bryophyta of North America Category:Moss genera Category:Grimmiales Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
